><p>该研究计划于 6 月上半月发表，彭博社看到了该研究，详细描述了从 2000 年到 2000 年的 30 多年来，对任何被怀疑是同性恋的军人实施的电击转换疗法、侵入性医学检查和政治迫害, 当禁止在军队服役的同性恋人员被解除时。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" subscriptions-action="subscribe" subscriptions-service="subscribe.google.com" subscriptions-display="true" subscriptions-decorate="">订阅</div><div class="dm__m"><span>或</span><a href="https://subscribe.scmp.com/">探索我们的计划</a></div></div></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.loggedIn" class="dm__s"><span class="default-meter__signin-text">已经是订户？</span> <div id="sign-in-link-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" class="dm__l2" subscriptions-action="login" subscriptions-service="subscribe.google.com" subscriptions-display="true">登录</div></div><hr class="vertical-line vertical-line--bottom"></div></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 14:39:12 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.scmp.com/news/world/europe/article/3221994/stain-british-lgbtq-veterans-were-subjected-conversion-therapy-and-witch-hunts-report-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid><link/> https://www.scmp.com/news/world/europe/article/3221994/stain-british-lgbtq-veterans-were-subjected-conversion-therapy-and-witch-hunts-report-says?utm_source=rss_feed<author><![CDATA[Bloomberg]]></author><category>消息</category><category>世界</category><category>英国</category><category>性别</category><category>5050</category><category>同志</category><category>人权</category><category>“污点”：英国 LGBTQ 退伍军人受到皈依治疗和政治迫害</category><category>报告说</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tech war: major Micron client in China retracts Shanghai IPO application three days before Beijing opened cybersecurity investigation into US firm]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>中国固态硬盘 (SSD) 制造商北京 Memblaze 科技有限公司<a href="https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3221682/timeline-how-micron-went-welcome-business-partner-china-target-national-cybersecurity-probe?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221978_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="dcea0073-de3d-4c7d-bfc6-9298c5f3cfa7" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">是美光科技</a>存储芯片的主要买家，该公司于 3 月下旬撤回了<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/shanghai?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221978_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="07f7fb18-e092-4d77-ab32-771a2db08478" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">在上海</a>的公开上市，就<a href="https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3215622/tech-war-china-hits-back-american-chip-firms-regulator-launches-cybersecurity-probe-microns-products?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221978_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="8c464f0d-a38f-4b05-bb0c-1c04ad0b48e0" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">在北京对这家美国公司展开网络安全调查的</a>前几天。</p><p>虽然没有证据表明 Memblaze 的<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/ipo?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221978_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="22e6e90f-4759-49f9-8f4d-b87379c7dddb" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">首次公开募股</a>流产与美光有直接联系，但这家中国公司放弃上市的举动与美国公司接受网络空间下的网络安全审查办公室的调查接近 - 三天 -中国行政当局 (CAC) 以国家安全为由。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" subscriptions-action="subscribe" subscriptions-service="subscribe.google.com" subscriptions-display="true" subscriptions-decorate="">订阅</div><div class="dm__m"><span>或</span><a href="https://subscribe.scmp.com/">探索我们的计划</a></div></div></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.loggedIn" class="dm__s"><span class="default-meter__signin-text">已经是订户？</span> <div id="sign-in-link-11-large" role="button" tabinde